-thumbnail wp-post-image\" alt=\"Quelles en-ttes de scurit indispensables pour votre WordPress ?\" /></p>On nest jamais trop port sur la scurit avec WordPress. Non pas que notre CMS prfr soit vulnrable. Non. Cest juste quil propulse plus du tiers de la totalit des sites internet. En ce qui concerne les sites web spcifiquement ralis par un CMS, on le retrouve mme dans deux tiers des cas. Ainsi, cest [&hellip;]<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpfr/~4/l4GPstFP1xw\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:83:\"https://wpformation.com/quelles-en-tetes-de-securite-indispensables-pour-wordpress/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:84:\"\n		        \n		        \n		        \n		        \n		        \n		        \n		        \n		    \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:4:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"Ordre du jour de la 1re runion documentation du 11 janvier 2021\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/wpfr/~3/vMtZFwApWzY/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:98:\"https://fr.wordpress.org/team/2021/01/06/ordre-du-jour-1ere-reunion-documentation-11-janvier-2021/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 06 Jan 2021 20:29:45 +0